<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٧٣٨ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ ,<span class="c5"> عَنْ قَتَادَةَ فِي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{مِنَ الْكِبَرِ عِتِيًّا}</span> <span class="c4">[مريم: ٨]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«سِنًّا»</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«وَكَانَ ابْنُ بِضْعٍ وَسَبْعِينَ سَنَةً»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>